# Day 10 – CloudWatch Alarms

##  Goal
Create CloudWatch Alarms to monitor EC2 metrics and send notifications.

##  Steps Taken
1. Selected EC2 CPUUtilization metric.
2. Created alarm with threshold: CPU > 80% for 5 minutes.
3. Configured SNS topic and confirmed email subscription.
4. Installed stress tool on Amazon Linux 2023:
   ```bash
   sudo dnf install stress -y
   stress --cpu 2 --timeout 300
